# Machine Learning Project

## Project Overview
This project demonstrates a basic machine learning workflow using Python and Jupyter Notebook. The project involves loading a dataset, performing data preprocessing, training machine learning models, and evaluating their performance.

The main objective is to understand how machine learning models can be applied to analyze data and make predictions.

## Features
- Data loading and exploration
- Data cleaning and preprocessing
- Feature selection
- Machine learning model training
- Model evaluation

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Jupyter Notebook

